msgid "Contact your co-Trainer(s) and decide who will teach what."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:22
msgid ""
"Create an event Etherpad (using the Etherpad template) or Google Doc "
"(using the Google Doc template) and a workshop website (using the "
"training template).  Note the Google Doc is not currently maintained and "
"may not be in sync with lesson materials."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:23
msgid "Send Etherpad/Google Doc and website links to training@carpentries.org."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:25
msgid "One week before the event"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:26
msgid "Plan logistics with co-Trainer(s)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:27
msgid ""
"Review (or set aside time closer to the event to review) the pre-"
"assessment survey results for your workshop"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:28
msgid "If teaching remotely:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:29
#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:81
msgid "Get acquanted with using Zoom for videoconferencing."
