#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:30
msgid ""
"Test videoconferencing set up with co-Trainer(s) using login credentials "
"provided."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:31
msgid ""
"Decide with co-Trainer(s) whether all Trainers should be present for the "
"full event or if you will log on during your scheduled teaching times "
"only."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:32
msgid ""
"Make a copy of the Virtual Minute Cards template and personalize for your"
" event."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:33
msgid "If teaching in person:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:34
msgid ""
"Confirm with your host that breakout rooms are available or make an "
"alternate plan"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:35
msgid ""
"Create a plan for printing handouts & determine who will bring sticky "
"notes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:36
msgid ""
"Make sure you're prepared for the audiovisual setup in your room with the"
" correct dongles/connectors etc."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:37
msgid ""
"Check on availability/timing of coffee, lunch, or any other details that "
"matter to you"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:39
msgid "During the event"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:40
msgid "Take attendance."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:41
msgid ""
"Remind member trainees to fill out application (Open Training applicants "
"have already done this)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:42
msgid ""
"Remind trainees to sign up for demo, discussion (links in checkout "
"checklist)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:43
msgid ""
"Monitor the Etherpad / Google Doc for questions and responses to "
"exercises."
